 pain and support waste elimination.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Celery 3000 Tablets All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Celery 3000 Size Size 50 tablets Blackmores Celery 3000 contains celery and celery seed oil, traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to assist body waste elimination, relieve mild rheumatic aches and pains, and support healthy digestion. It also relieves symptoms of mild arthritis and occasional episodes of gout. Good health changes everything - support your body&#x27;s natural elimination processes with Blackmores Celery 3000. Product Format Tablet Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Mild Rheumatic Pain Gout Symptoms No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Dairy No Added Soya Bean Benefits & How To Use Benefits Contains celery extract and celery seed oil. Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: Reduce the symptoms of occasional episodes of gout Reduce mild rheumatic aches and pains. Assist body waste elimination. Supports healthy digestive system function. Dosage Adults Take 1 to 2 tablets a day, with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, worsen or episodes become more frequent, talk to your medical practitioner. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. If you have pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings Contains celery extract and celery seed oil. Traditionally used in Western herbal medicine to: Reduce the symptoms of occasional episodes of gout Reduce mild rheumatic aches and pains. Assist body waste elimination. Supports healthy digestive system function. Adults Take 1 to 2 tablets a day, with meals or as prescribed by a health professional. Children under 18 years old Only as prescribed by a health professional. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. If symptoms persist, worsen or episodes become more frequent, talk to your medical practitioner. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. If you have pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your