and supporting vitamins and minerals.","descriptionTh":"สูตรพรีเมี่ยมเพื่อสุขภาพดวงตา ประกอบด้วยลูทีน ซีแซนทีน ผงเก๋ากี้ และวิตามินแร่ธาตุสนับสนุน","extractedText":"Lutein Pro+ by Swisse | Premium Wellness Supplement in Thailand - Swisse Thailand Skip to content Products Back Products Beauty Eye Care Gummies Gut Health Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Moisturisers Multivitamins Serums Skin Super Fruits & Herbs All Products Range Wellness Beauty Skincare About Back Our Story Ingredients Wellness Hub Sign in Search Cart (0) Cart empty Your cart is empty Continue shopping     svg]:w-full group-hover:text-uiGrey\"> Home / Lutein Pro+   Skip to product information Open media 1 in modal Open media 2 in modal Open media 3 in modal Swisse Lutein Pro+ SWISSE LUTEIN PRO+ is a premium formula with 7 essential nutrients (vitamins, minerals, and antioxidants) designed to support and restore eye health. With Lutein and Zeaxanthin, it helps filter blue light, especially from prolonged screen exposure on mobile phones, tablets, and computers. Swisse is committed to contributing positively to the needs of society and the planet, and we are the carbon neutral company. #LuteinPro+ Sale price 760 ฿ Where to buy Buy at TikTok Buy at Shopee Buy at Lazada Buy at Line Benefits Lutein, a type of carotenoid, helps filter blue light in the eyes. Lutein, Zeaxanthin, and Goji Berry Powder provide powerful antioxidant properties. Key Ingredients Each tablet contains: Lutein 12 mg Zeaxanthin 2.4 mg Goji Berry Powder 50 mg Vitamin C 30 mg Vitamin E 6.2 mg Zinc 5 mg Copper 301 mcg Directions and Warnings DIRECTIONS: 1 tablet daily. Take during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional. WARNINGS: Children, pregnant women, and patient with kidney tone should not consume. Should eat a variety of the five categories of food in appropriate proportions STORAGE: Store below 25C, in a cool, dry place. Do not use if cap seal is broken. Reasons to love us We have been developing science-based formulas using premium ingredients sourced from around the world for over 50 years. We believe in natural ingredients being our hero ingredients. We also pursue the latest research findings to formulate our advanced product ranges and consistently strive to anticipate consumer demand. Backed by science Premium quality formula 50+ year heritage Certified B-Corp We are B-Corp Certified B Corps are for-profit companies that meet high standards of social and environmental performance, transparency, and accountability. Swisse is a brand of H&H Group, a certified B Corp. We feel honoured to be part of a global community using business as a force for good. Frequently Asked Questions Do we need to take vitamin supplements? The key is to ensure that we get a complete and balanced intake of nutrients each day. However, due to lifestyle limitations and dietary choices, we may not always receive the necessary nutrients in adequate amounts. In such cases, dietary supplements can be beneficial. Can Swisse products be taken alongside medication or medical treatments? Each individual has different nutritional and medicinal needs. If you are unsure whether Swisse products are suitable for you, it is best to consult a doctor. Please note that dietary supplements do not prevent, alter, or replace medical treatment or a well-balanced diet. What is the best time to take vitamins? Some supplements work best when taken with food, while others are more effective on an empty stomach. It is essential to follow the instructions on the label to maximize the benefits of each product. How long do dietary supplements last? In general, dietary supplements have a shelf life of approximately two years from the manufacturing date. Where does Swisse source its ingredients? We carefully select and source high-quality, premium-grade ingredients from around the world to ensure that only the best components go into our products. Where are Swisse products manufactured? Most of our products are manufactured in Australia. Please refer to the product packaging for the specific country of origin. The recommended dosage on the label applies to which age group? The recommended dosage is intended for individuals aged 18 and above. You may also like Swisse Ultivite Essential Multivitamin Sale price 990 ฿ Swisse Ultivite Multivitamin with Folic Acid Sale price 650 ฿ Our Products Beauty Eye Care Gut Health Gummies Immunity Joints, Bones, & Muscles Multivitamins Super Fruits & Herbs Skincare About Swisse Our Story Ingredients Help & Support FAQs Contact Us Privacy Policy Follow Us &copy; Swisse Thailand , 2026 Choosing a selection results in a full page refresh.\n\nBenefits Lutein, a type of carotenoid, helps filter blue light in the eyes. Lutein, Zeaxanthin, and Goji Berry Powder provide powerful antioxidant properties.\n\nKey Ingredients Each tablet contains: Lutein 12 mg Zeaxanthin 2.4 mg Goji Berry Powder 50 mg Vitamin C 30 mg Vitamin E 6.2 mg Zinc 5 mg Copper 301 mcg\n\nDirections and Warnings DIRECTIONS: 1 tablet daily. Take during or immediately after a meal, or as directed by a healthcare professional.","productOffers":[{"url":"https://vt.tiktok.com/ZMBa1GBYF/?page=TikTokShop","label":"Buy at TikTok","status":"active","network":"swisse_where_to_buy","linkType":"direct","platform":"tiktok","priority":100},{"url":"https://shopee.co.th/swisse_thailand","label":"Buy at Shopee","status":"active","network":"swisse_where_to_buy","linkType":"direct","platform":"shopee","priority":99},{"url":"https://s.lazada.co.th/s.vPVfK","label":"Buy at Lazada","status":"active","network":"swisse_where_to_buy","linkType":"direct","platform":"lazada","priority":98},{"url":"https://shop.line.me/@swisse","label":"Buy at Line","status":"active","network":"swisse_where_to_buy","linkType":"direct","platform":"line","priority":97},{"url":"https://www.tiktok.com/@swisse_thailand","label":"Where to buy","status":"active","network":"swisse_where_to_buy","linkType":"direct","platform":"