l Oil Mini Capsules All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Krill Oil Mini Size Size 60 capsules Blackmores Krill Oil Mini is specially formulated in an easy-to-swallow, mini-sized capsule with a comprehensive blend of omega-3 from krill oil, astaxanthin, and vitamin E. Formulated with 8 key benefits to support joint, heart, brain, skin, immune and cardiovascular health and healthy liver function. Additionally, its antioxidant ingredients, astaxanthin and vitamin E, help reduce free radicals formed in the body. Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. Support For Brain Health Immune System Health Liver & Detoxification Joint Health Skin Health No Added Yeast No Added Dairy Halal Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits Easy to swallow, mini sized capsule. Supports joint, heart, brain, skin and immune system health. Supports cardiovascular health. Supports healthy liver function. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Astaxanthin cultivated from the waters of Kailua-Kona in Hawaii. Wild caught krill from a certified sustainable fishery. Dosage Adults To support general health and well-being: Take 2 capsules once a day. To support immune system health and function : Take 3 capsules once a day. As a source of omega-3 and choline to support brain, heart, joint, skin and healthy liver function: Take 4 capsules a day. Do not exceed 6 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Warnings Keep out of reach of children. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Always read the labels and follow the directions for use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Contains crustacea, soya bean and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Easy to swallow, mini sized capsule. Supports joint, heart, brain, skin and immune system health. Supports cardiovascular health. Supports healthy liver function. Antioxidant to reduce free radicals formed in the body. Astaxanthin cultivated from the waters of Kailua-Kona in Hawaii. Wild caught krill from a certified sustainable fishery. Adults To support general health and well-being: Take 2 capsules once a day. To support immune system health and function : Take 3 capsules once a day. As a source of omega-3 and choline to support brain, heart, joint, skin and healthy liver function: Take 4 capsules a day. Do not exceed 6 capsules in 24 hours. Take with food. Keep out of reach of children. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Always read the labels and follow the directions for use. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. If you are pregnant or breastfeeding, talk to your health professional before use. Contains crustacea, soya bean and sulfites. Ingredients Euphausia superba oil (Antarctic krill oil) 500 mg containing eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) 60 mg containing docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) 27.5 mg equivalent astaxanthin 50 micrograms equivalent phosphatidyl choline 150 mg Astaxanthin esters extracted from Haematococcus pluvialis 7 mg equivalent astaxanthin 500 micrograms d-alpha-tocopheryl (vitamin E 7.45 IU) 5 mg Krill Oil Mini Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Regi