ean No Added Dairy Vegan Certified Benefits & How To Use Benefits For people who: Struggle to relax and feel calm. Have a racing mind and feel tense. Have a stressful life. Want to support their lifestyle relaxation techniques. Want the convenience of a once-a-day dose to help them relax. Dosage Adults Take 2 tablets once a day as required. Maximum of 2 tablets per day. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Benefits Dosage Warnings For people who: Struggle to relax and feel calm. Have a racing mind and feel tense. Have a stressful life. Want to support their lifestyle relaxation techniques. Want the convenience of a once-a-day dose to help them relax. Adults Take 2 tablets once a day as required. Maximum of 2 tablets per day. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. May cause drowsiness, if affected do not drive a vehicle or operate machinery. If symptoms persist, talk to your health professional. If you have pre-existing conditions or are on any medications always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per tablet: Lavandula angustifolia (lavender) extract dry conc. 150 mg equivalent dry flower 600 mg Humulus lupulus (hops) extract dry conc. 33.3 mg equivalent dry strobile 250 mg Passiflora incarnata (passionflower) extract dry conc. 50 mg equivalent dry herb 250 mg Avena sativa (oa