and mild osteoarthritis.","descriptionTh":null,"extractedText":"Blackmores Lyprinol Double Capsules All Products Shop All Products New Products Best Sellers Vegan Certified Women&#x27;s Health Men&#x27;s Health Kid&#x27;s Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition By Category Arthritis, Joint & Bone Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutritional Oils Heart Health Infant & Toddler Nutrition Kids&#x27; Health Men&#x27;s Health Multivitamins Muscle Support Nails, Hair & Skin Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health By Ingredient Calcium CoQ10 Curcumin Echinacea Fish Oil & Omega 3 Glucosamine Iron Magnesium Probiotics Selenium Vitamin B Vitamin C Vitamin D Vitamin E Zinc Health Hub By Categories By Type Latest Articles Action Plans Arthritis, Bone & Joint Beauty & Skincare Brain & Cognitive Health Cold, Flu & Immunity Digestive & Gut Health Energy Everyday Health Eye Health Fish & Nutrition Oils Heart & Cardiovascular Health Kids & Infant Health Men&#x27;s Health Muscle Support & Fitness Preconception, Pregnancy & Breastfeeding Recipes Stress Relief & Sleep Support Women&#x27;s Health Action Plans Articles Recipes Latest Articles About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Pillars Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Contact us Ask A Naturopath Our Newsroom Blackmores Subscribe Search Home Chevron Icon Horizontal products Chevron Icon Horizontal Blackmores Lyprinol® Double Size Size 30 capsules Blackmores Lyprinol® Double provides 100 mg of specialised non-GMO green-lipped mussel marine oil per capsule. This high-strength formula helps relieve inflammation, reduce symptoms of mild osteoarthritis, and support general health and wellbeing. The oil is extracted using a cold-process method that preserves delicate marine lipid complexes, ensuring their structural integrity and natural anti-inflammatory activity. Designed for convenient once-daily dosing, it’s ideal for adults managing mild arthritis symptoms or seeking ongoing support for joint comfort and mobility. With no exposure to high heat or solvents, Lyprinol® Double delivers a clean, stable extract from New Zealand waters. Taken daily with food, it’s a well-tolerated and science-informed option for proactive joint care. Good health changes everything - support your joint health naturally and effectively with Blackmores Lyprinol® Double. (137 words) Product Format Capsule Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Read the warnings before purchase. No Added Yeast No Added Gluten No Added Wheat No Added Dairy Benefits & How To Use Benefits Reduces symptoms of mild arthritis. Relieves inflammation. Double the amount of oil compared to the original 50 mg capsule. Non-GMO specialised NZ marine oil extract of green-lipped mussel. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Dosage Adults Initially, take 2 capsules 2 times a day for up to 8 weeks. Then reduce dose to 1 capsule two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Warnings Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Not recommended for people with seafood allergies. If symptoms persist see your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains mollusc, soya bean products and sulfites. Benefits Dosage Warnings Reduces symptoms of mild arthritis. Relieves inflammation. Double the amount of oil compared to the original 50 mg capsule. Non-GMO specialised NZ marine oil extract of green-lipped mussel. Maintains general health and wellbeing. Adults Initially, take 2 capsules 2 times a day for up to 8 weeks. Then reduce dose to 1 capsule two times a day, or as prescribed by a health professional. Take with food. Always read the label and follow the directions for use. Do not use during pregnancy or breastfeeding. Not recommended for people with seafood allergies. If symptoms persist see your health professional. If you have any pre-existing conditions or are on any medications, always talk to your health professional before use. Some products should be ceased at least two weeks before any elective surgery, please confirm with your health professional. Contains mollusc, soya bean products and sulfites. The Blackmores Difference Ingredients Active ingredients per capsule: Marine PCSO-524® Oil extract (Green lipped mussel oil) 100 mg a specialied extract of NZ Perna canaliculus Lyprinol® Double Reviews Let&#x27;s stay in touch Instagram Facebook TikTok LinkedIn Back To Top About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom About Blackmores About Blackmores Our Heritage Our Approach Our Impact Our Sustainability Approach Our People & Culture Our Careers Our Ambassadors & Partners Our Newsroom Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education Our Brands & Products Shop Our Products Shop Best Sellers BioCeuticals Blackmores Professional Blackmores Institute Blackmores Education International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam International Markets China Hong Kong SAR iHerb Indonesia Korea Malaysia New Zealand Singapore Taiwan Region Thailand Vietnam Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Terms & Policies Privacy Policy & Practices Terms Of Purchase Terms of Service Posting Guidelines Social Media House Rules Contacts & FAQs Report a Suspecte